title: NewSoftwares Folder Lock v7.6.1
description:
NewSoftwares Folder Lock v7.6.1

Data Security Software powered by 
AES 256-Bit Military Grade encryption!
Developed for Windows PC Users

What is Folder Lock?
Folder Lock lets you password-protect files, folders and drives; encrypt your important files on-the-fly; backup them in real-time; protect portable drives; shred files & drives and clean history. Folder Lock is the most downloaded file-security application with more than 25 million users. It works on 32-bit and 64-bit versions of Windows 10, 8, 7, Vista, XP.

Lock files & folders
Hide your private images, documents & videos with click of a button.
Encrypt your files
Encrypt confidential files & folders in Lockers on-the-fly. Lockers are portable.
Backup Lockers
Backup and sync your encrypted files in Lockers securely to secure cloud.
Portable Lockers
Create portable self-executable Lockers in USB Drives, CDs/DVDs, Emails.
Make Wallets
Make digital wallets to securely save real-life Cards like Credit Cards and SSN.
Shred files
Permanently delete files on your computer so they are unrecoverable.
History Clean
Clean Windows History and tracks of PC activity and redundant files on your PC.
Settings
Password Security, Stealth Mode, Hack Attempt Monitoring & Auto Protect.

Official Website: http://www.newsoftwares.net/folderlock/
